    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I think the answer which I have given meets the hon. Gentleman on that point.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-bb40486a-2118-4dad-9c89-0fd7fe648952" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
